parameters: Finally awake, are you, Resistance's cyborg?
Your comrades told us everything, Esuka-chan.
Ah! Everyone, everyone is safe, right?

Gyahahaha! There's no way you could escape alive!
We've captured you again, along with the fools who
came to rescue you!

Poor thing, our interrogation is quite harsh, you
might even die...?

...! I'll never forgive you! I'll definitely beat
you down!

Oh, scary, scary. We can't have you, Esuka-chan,
acting out like this.

This is what we call an electronic information
transfer solution used by the military's
intelligence department. It's a wonderful thing
that transfers information and structure when
splashed onto electronic devices. It solidifies
quickly, so it's convenient for recovery. Well,
it's an incredibly handy jelly.

Ugh... Don't splash that gross, slimy stuff on
me...?
Don't worry, don't worry, this is how it's done!

Since you're in human form, it's more beneficial
to shove it inside you.
Ugh...! My stomach, it's going to burst.

Gyahahaha, you look like a frog, Esuka-chan.
You're in quite a state.

Oh, it seems the transcription has already
started. It might sting a bit, but bear with it,
okay?

Even for a cyborg, it must be tough to have your
body burned from the inside, isn't it?

(W-what... It feels like my consciousness is
gathering in my stomach... It's nauseating...)

I see, it's not just the mechanical structure, but
it seems that even Esuka-chan's personality has
begun to be transcribed. As expected of a cyborg.

Ohh!? T-this, along with my consciousness... is it
going to fly out!?

Oh, oh, such a strained face, you seem to be in
pain. Shall I help you?

Huh!? If you do anything unnecessary, I'll kill
you! I'll kill you, okay!?
Oh, there it is, there it is~
(W-what... that, m-my body...⁉ So now I'm...)

Esuka's consciousness was completely reflected in
the transcription solution. She was being toyed
with on the hand of the modified soldier, unable
to move a muscle.

From now on, I'll thoroughly examine you from
corner to corner, and after that, yes, I might
just modify you into a fleshlight! Gyahahahaha!

It's a waste to let such a body go unused. Maybe I
should implant the pseudo-personality I created
for prostitutes.
(D-don't put anything weird in my body...!)
Gyahahaha, I'll modify you into a comfort cyborg.
(No! Don't make me swallow such a thing...!)

Soon your personality will be firmly established.
You'll work hard for the empire.
